{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 58,
  "title": "第五十八章（順化）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "其政悶悶，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其民醇醇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其政察察，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其民缺缺。"
    },
    {
      "text": "禍兮福之所倚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "福兮禍之所伏。"
    },
    {
      "text": "孰知其極，"
    },
    {
      "text": "其無正，"
    },
    {
      "text": "正復為奇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "善復為訞。"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之迷，其日固久。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人方而不割，"
    },
    {
      "text": "廉而不害，"
    },
    {
      "text": "直而不肆，"
    },
    {
      "text": "光而不曜。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其政教寬大，悶悶昧昧，似若不明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "政教寬大，故民醇醇富厚，相親睦也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其政教急疾，言決於口，聽決於耳也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "政教急疾。民不聊生。故缺缺日以踈薄。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "倚，因也。夫福因禍而生，人遭禍而能悔過責己，修道行善，則禍去福來。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禍伏匿於福中，人得福而為驕恣，則福去禍來。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禍福更相生，誰能知其窮極時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無，不也。謂人君不正其身，其無國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奇，詐也。人君不正，下雖正，復化上為詐也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善人皆復化上為訞祥也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人君迷惑失正以來，其日已固久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人行方正者，欲以率下，不以割截人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人廉清，欲以化民，不以傷害人也。今則不然，正己以害人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "肆，申也。聖人雖直，曲己從人，不自申也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人雖有獨見之明，當如闇昧，不以曜亂人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
